    "template": "content",
    "texts": [
     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"Most of the routes on our bus network are put out to tender. If you want to run a bus, coach or tours service outside of our network, you'll need to apply for a London Service Permit.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     ".",
     "{\"template\":\"listgroup\",\"style\":\"nocard\",\"links\":[{\"title\":\"London Service Permit  Bulletin -  Monday 24 February 2020\",\"url\":\"/cdn/static/cms/documents/lsp-bulletin.pdf\",\"icon\":\"download\",\"size\":\"PDF 0.51MB\",\"image\":{}}],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Apply for a London Service Permit\"}",
     "Before you complete this form make sure you have all the relevant details to hand:",
     "{\"template\":\"bulletlist\",\"items\":[\"Personal/licence details\",\"Route/service descriptions (including stopping points)\",\"Vehicle details\",\"Disability information\",\"Health and safety documentation\"]}",
     "We require a minimum of three months' notice of the proposed start date of the service. If roads are currently not served by local bus services, or new stopping and terminal points are proposed, a longer notice period is desirable.",
     "We may use the data in your application form for research purposes.",
     "{\"template\":\"start-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"end-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Modify or cancel an application\"}",
     "Before you complete this form make sure you have all the relevant details to hand:",
     "{\"template\":\"bulletlist\",\"items\":[\"Personal/licence details\",\"LSP number\",\"Declaration\"]}",
     "{\"template\":\"start-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"end-row\",\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Guidance documents\"}",
     "{\"template\":\"listgroup\",\"style\":\"nocard\",\"links\":[{\"title\":\"London Service Permit guidance document\",\"url\":\"/cdn/static/cms/documents/lsp-guidance-document.pdf\",\"icon\":\"download\",\"size\":\"PDF 55KB\",\"image\":{}},{\"title\":\"London Service Permit explanatory note\",\"url\":\"/cdn/static/cms/documents/lsp-explanatory-note.pdf\",\"icon\":\"download\",\"size\":\"PDF 182KB\",\"image\":{}}],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Contact us\"}",
     "If you cannot apply online, or have any questions about London Service Permits, please contact the Licensing Team:",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eEmail:\u003c/strong\u003e  \u003ca href=\"mailto:lsp@tfl.gov.uk\"\u003elsp@tfl.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "\u003cstrong\u003eAddress:\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cbr /\u003eBus Service Licensing and Permitting\u003cbr /\u003eLicensing, Regulation and Charging\u003cbr /\u003e4th Floor, Zone 4G3\u003cbr /\u003e5 Endeavour Square\u003cbr /\u003eStratford, London E20 1JN"
